headline: Is Ford Stock a Buy Now?
summary: Its Pro segment is seeing good growth prospects, a double-digit operating margin, and recurring revenue stream.  Economic conditions, tariffs, and labor disputes are some external factors that can have a huge impact on Ford.  Detroit automaker Ford Motor Company (NYSE: F) is one of them.
